org.contentmine.cproject.args

Class ArgIterator

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.contentmine.cproject.args.ArgIterator

  • public class ArgIterator
extends java.lang.Object
    wraps ListIterator as this causes reflection problems. Tokens of form -[digit]... are treated as numbers Tokens of form -[letter]... are treated as flags
    Author:
    pm286
